body:
Compat issues with assembly Microsoft.Bot.Builder:
MembersMustExist : Member 'Microsoft.Bot.Builder.BotFrameworkAdapter.GetAadTokensAsync(Microsoft.Bot.Builder.ITurnContext, System.String, System.String[], System.String)' does not exist in the implementation but it does exist in the contract.
MembersMustExist : Member 'Microsoft.Bot.Builder.BotFrameworkAdapter.GetTokenStatusAsync(Microsoft.Bot.Builder.ITurnContext, System.String, System.String)' does not exist in the implementation but it does exist in the contract.
InterfacesShouldHaveSameMembers : Interface member 'Microsoft.Bot.Builder.Integration.IAdapterIntegration.ContinueConversationAsync(System.String, Microsoft.Bot.Schema.ConversationReference, Microsoft.Bot.Builder.BotCallbackHandler, System.Threading.CancellationToken)' is present in the implementation but not in the contract.
